flowchart TD
    Write[Client writes value v2\nto Node A] --> NodeA[(Node A\nvalue: v2)]

    NodeA -->|Replicate| NodeB[(Node B\nvalue: v1 stale)]
    NodeA -->|Replicate| NodeC[(Node C\nvalue: v1 stale)]

    NodeB --> ReadB{Read from Node B}
    ReadB -->|Before sync| StaleRead[Returns v1 - stale read]
    ReadB -->|After sync| FreshB[Returns v2]

    NodeB -->|Receives update| SyncB[Node B applies v2]
    NodeC -->|Receives update| SyncC[Node C applies v2]

    SyncB --> Converged{All nodes synced?}
    SyncC --> Converged
    Converged -->|Yes| Consistent[Consistent state\nAll nodes return v2]
    Converged -->|No| Wait[Wait for propagation]
    Wait --> Converged
